commit e57c74f9ef19201f72c106f2c347596f40229936
Author: Jia Tan <jiat0218@gmail.com>
Date:   2023-03-16 21:41:09 +0800

    Doc: Update PACKAGERS with details about liblzma API docs install.

 PACKAGERS | 22 ++++++++++++++++------
