    xz: Refactor to remove is_empty_filename().
    
    Long ago it was used in list.c too but nowadays it's needed
    only in io_open_src() so it's nicer to avoid a separate function.

 src/xz/file_io.c |  4 +++-
 src/xz/util.c    | 12 ------------
